  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4993307/" class="title-link">读伊萨克•巴别尔《红色骑兵军》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4993307"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/renrenzhenzhen/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1487783-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/renrenzhenzhen/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">吉祥如意</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-06-18"
      class="main-meta">2011-06-18 12:11:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4993307_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  严格来说，巴别尔的《红色骑兵军》并非一部短篇小说集，而是叙事散文集。在这里，有头有尾的故事仅占半数，简洁紧凑的叙述往往用于表现场景和行动，如同一系列速写，寥寥几笔勾勒出战争背景下的生活和人性，其形象之生动独特、笔触之冷峻老辣、内容之恣肆酷烈，均令人过目难忘...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4993307/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">38有用 / 1没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            浙江文艺出版社2009版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
